snippet: American forces captured a Libyan militant, known by his nom de guerre, Abu Anas al-Libi, who had been indicted in 2000 for his role in the 1998 bombings of the United States embassies in Kenya and Tanzania.
lead_paragraph: American forces captured a Libyan militant, known by his nom de guerre, Abu Anas al-Libi, who had been indicted in 2000 for his role in the 1998 bombings of the United States embassies in Kenya and Tanzania.
